&lt;p&gt;And remember: we don’t expect you to meet every single requirement. If you’re excited by this role, &lt;strong&gt;we encourage you to apply!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GoCardless are seeking a self-motivated, curious, and inspired brand designer to join our design team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are at an exciting point in our journey, expanding our brand footprint and enhancing our product experience. This role is ideal for a proactive designer who is excited to contribute to a growing design team and make a significant impact in shaping the future of the GoCardless brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Must have skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
