&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI: &lt;/strong&gt;You are familiar with and enthusiastic about the role AI plays in design. Whether generating assets, using it to expedite processes or building your own tool, you see its use as a force multiplier.&lt;/li&gt;
