&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Familiarity with motion design tools (such as After Effects, Jitter, Cavalry, Rive or equivalent):&lt;/strong&gt; Experience in creating micro animations and interactive elements is important for us.&lt;/li&gt;
